OOC:( Megatron, Scorponok and DarkMouse are at the Destron Base. Megatron is 
waiting for Panzertron so they can talk. DarkMouse said that she smelled a 
trap while they were all waiting for Panzertron to appear.  Scorponok stayed 
with Megatron while DarkMouse went looking around.  The only door she found 
open was a CR chamber room.  She was headed back to the room where Megatron 
was when she heard a noise behind a door.  She listened and heard nothing so 
she porcceded back down the hallway to the room where Megatron and Scorponok 
were.)
